      "span_text": "While SIR contains mostly artificially-generated faults, iBUGS  provides a semi-automated approach for extracting benchmarks with real bugs from project histories, using an approach based on commit messages and regression tests. iBUGS' idea of using the regression tests as a semi-automatic bug confirmation mechanism could be borrowed by Covrig whenever fixes are accompanied by tests, reducing the manual effort needed to apply it to new projects.",
